author: Adam Savage’s Tested
description:
Given the surge in generative AI, does Adam feel that the barriers to entry for creatives can be TOO Low? How sturdy is Adam's hole-y chair? Has Adam ever done a a scan using his phone's Lidar? In this live stream excerpt, Adam answers these questions from Tested members Oz.DeLorean, curry-surfer and Henry_C_7316, whom we thank for their support.
